# Light theme only

This app must always use the light (white) UI. Do not:

- Add `dark` class to `document.documentElement` or rely on `prefers-color-scheme` for app chrome
- Reintroduce theme switchers (`light` / `dark` / `system`) for the main layout
- Use `next-themes` or similar for global appearance unless it is locked to light only

`src/index.css` `:root` tokens define the canonical palette; `body` uses `bg-background` from those variables.
